reviewText: Some part of the DVD is damage.
UNA PRESENTACION DE ESTE GRUPO ARGENTINO, EN LOS CUALES PRESENTAN CORTOS NUEVOS Y RETOMAN ALGUNOS CLASICOS, DURA CASI DOS HORAS LAS CUALES SIN DUDA ALGUNA SERAN DE MUCHA RISA.
i got the item really quik, it works great and the video is of good quality. the box is new never used before!

This DVD is one of the latest ones created by the genius group Les Luthiers.
I deffinitively recommend it if you know spanish and want to laugh untill you cry :)

This is Les Luthiers, an awesome/hilarious show just like the others, simply great.

One more to complete my collection :)

A+++
